<F P=106> [By Reporter Chen Jiaying (7115 1367 3841)] </F>
  [Text] Lisbon, 4 Jan (XINHUA) -- Portuguese Foreign 
Minister Durao Barroso said today that "quite satisfactory 
progress" was made in the development of relations between 
Portugal and China in 1993. 
  He made this remark while speaking about China at a forum on 
