<F P=103> HK1101114894 </F>
<F P=104>  Guangzhou Guangdong People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] This morning provincial party Secretary Xie Fei 
hosted a provincial meeting on exchanging experiences in 
conducting the month of courtesy, safety, health, and service. 
[passage omitted] 
  After listening to feedback on progress in this activity, 
Xie 
Fei made important remarks. He said: The the month of 
courtesy, safety, health, and service has practical and 
far-reaching significance. Do not think that this activity is 
