<H3> <TI>   `Leading Comrades' Attend CPPCC New Year Party </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1101124394 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0917 
GMT 1 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1101124394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By reporter Zou Aiguo (6760 1947 0948)] </F>
  [Excerpts] Beijing, 1 Jan (XINHUA) -- The Chinese People's 
Political Consultative Conference [CPPCC] National Committee 
held a new year reception at the CPPCC Auditorium this morning. 
  Leading comrades Jiang Zemin, Li Peng, Qiao Shi, Li Ruihuan, 
Zhu Rongji, Liu Huaqing, Hu Jintao, and Rong Yiren joined some 
400 people from all walks of life in the capital to celebrate 
the advent of the year 1994. 
  Li Ruihuan, chairman of the CPPCC National Committee, 
officiated at the reception. 
  In his speech, Jiang Zemin, general secretary of the CPC 
Central Committee, president of the state, and chairman of the 
Central Military Commission extended -- on behalf of the CPC 
Central Committee, the State Council, and the Central Military 
Commission -- warm solicitude and noble tribute to the 
democratic parties and patriotic personages without party 
affiliation; to workers, peasants, intellectuals and cadres of 
all nationalities across the country; and to Liberation Army 
commanders and fighters, Armed Police officers and men, and 
public security cadres and policemen; as well as sincere holiday 
greetings and best wishes to compatriots in Taiwan, Hong Kong 
and Macao, and overseas Chinese, and foreign friends who have 
concerned themselves with, supported, and assisted China's 
modernization construction. [passage omitted] 
  Also attending the reception were leading comrades: Ding 
Guangen, Li Lanqing, Yang Baibing, Zou Jiahua, Wei Jianxing, Wen 
Jiabao, Wang Hanbin, Ren Jianxin, Ni Zhifu, Chen Muhua, Fei 
Xiaotong, Sun Qimeng, Lei Jieqiong, Li Ximing, Wang Guangying, 
Cheng Siyuan, Lu Jiaxi, Buhe, Li Peiyao, Wu Jieping, Luo Gan, Wu 
Xueqian, Yang Rudai, Wang Zhaoguo, Seypidin Aze, Hong Xuezhi, 
Qian Weichang, Hu Sheng, Qian Zheng, and Sun Fuling. 
  Attending the reception were also officials from democratic 
parties and the All-China Federation of Industry and Commerce, 
members of the National People's Congress Standing Committee, 
members of the CPPCC National Committee Standing Committee in 
Beijing, officials from people's organizations, and celebrities 
from various circles. 
  Artists from the Central Nationalities Philharmonic 
Orchestra, the China Song and Dance Theatrical Company, and the 
Central Song and Dance Troupe staged colorful performances at 
the gathering. 

</TEXT>

