<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Almaty, January 11 (XINHUA) -- Kazakhstan's Defense 
Minister Sagadat Nurmagambetov is heading a military delegation 
to pay a four-day visit to China. 
  Upon his departure at the airport, Nurmagambetov told 
reporters that his visit would boost friendly relations between 
