<F P=100> Central Eurasia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Kazakh Defense Minister, Delegation Visit PRC </TI></H3>
<H4>   Meets Chi Haotian </H4>
<F P=102> OW1101134394 Beijing XINHUA in English 1312 GMT 11 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1101134394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, January 11 (XINHUA) -- Chi Haotian, Chinese 
State Councillor and defense minister, met with and hosted a 
banquet here this evening in honor of Visiting Kazakhstani 
Defense Minister Sagadat Nurmagambetov and his party. 
  This is the first visit to China by a defense minister of 
Kazakhstan since the country won its independence. 
  As Chi's guests, Nurmagambetov and his party arrived here 
this morning. In the afternoon, Chi hosted a welcoming ceremony 
for his Kazakh counterpart and held talks with him. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

